​Careers
Explore a world of opportunities: MDA is an equal opportunity employer committed to promoting diversity in the workplace
MDA has been connecting people with exciting and challenging careers since 1969. We have over 4,800 employees around the world: talented individuals from diverse backgrounds with a strong commitment to timely delivery of cost-effective solutions, with integrity, passion and pride.
At MDA, we believe that our personal and business success is the result of the diverse ideas, experiences, and personalities that our employees bring to work each day. We foster diversity and create a workplace where every employee can realize their full potential. We invite exceptional achievers from every background to bring their unique strengths to our organization.
To pursue career opportunities at MDA’s U.S. subsidiaries, please visit SSL Careers and MDA Information Systems LLC Careers.



















 











 




 




