MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


MDA





Type

Public


Traded as
TSX: MDA


Industry
Information technology services, Engineering services, Communications satellite


Founded
1969


Founder



John S. MacDonald
Werner (Vern) Dettwiler





Headquarters
Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada[1]



Key people




Howard L. Lance (President and CEO)
Daniel E. Friedmann (Former President and CEO)
Anil Wiresekara (EVP and CFO)





Revenue
$2.1 billion CAD (2016)[2]



