IntroductionMacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd.  - Strategy and SWOT Report, is a source of comprehensive company data and information. The report covers the company’s structure, operation, SWOT analysis, product and service offerings and corporate actions, providing a 360? view of the company.Features: - Detailed information on MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd. required for business and competitor intelligence needs - A study of the major internal and external factors affecting MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd. in the form of a SWOT analysis - An in-depth view of the business model of MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd. including a breakdown and examination of key business segments - Intelligence on MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd.’s mergers and acquisitions (M&A), strategic partnerships and alliances, capital raising, private equity transactions, and financial and legal advisors - News about MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd., such as business expansion, restructuring, and contract wins - Large number of easy-to-grasp charts and graphs that present important data and key trendsHighlights:MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd. (MDA or “the company”) is a communications and information company providing operational solutions to commercial and government organizations. The company primarily operates in the US and Canada. It is headquartered in British Columbia, Canada and employed about 4,800 people during 2014.  The company recorded revenues of C$2,098.8 million ($1,900.7 million) during the financial year ended December 2014 (FY2014), an increase of 15.4% over FY2013. The operating profit of the company was C$208 million ($188.4 million) in FY2014, an increase of 15.6% over FY2013. The net profit of the company was C$47.1 million ($42.7 million) in FY2014, a decrease of 55.1% as compared to FY2013.Reasons to Purchase: - Gain understanding of MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd. and the factors that influence its strategies  - Track strategic initiatives of the company and latest corporate news and actions  - Assess MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd. as a prospective partner, vendor or supplier - Support sales activities by understanding your customers' businesses better - Stay up to date on MacDonald, Dettwiler and Associates Ltd.’s business structure, strategy and prospects
	

